## Limitations
The analysis is limited by the availability of speculative and hypothetical scenarios, as the actual end of democracy is unprecedented in modern U.S. history. The perspectives gathered are primarily theoretical and may not fully capture the complexity of such a transition. Additionally, the reliance on online sources may introduce bias based on the authors' viewpoints and the platforms' editorial policies.